text: This mobile has been extensively remodeled. The Roof was replaced by Cascade Roofing in 2021 All Appliances were replaced in 2021 New furnace and deck in 2021 Fresh paint inside and out Flooring was all updated as well. A new pass bar with extra cabinetry was added to the kitchen space. This home also boasts large extra tip-out space great for a home office or extra large living room space. This lovely home is located in 55+ park in the last space, covered carport has a 10x10 storage unit and covered parking for 2. Nice private space in the back for patio furniture space to add gardening boxes. Quiet Park is near I-5 minutes from downtown MV and waterfront walking trails, Fairgrounds, and the community center.

Meticulously designed and built by a master carpenter as his personal residence, this home is a rare find and not to be missed. Set back from Chuckanut Drive and surrounded by farm fields, this 10-acre estate is a private, peaceful sanctuary. Soak in views of the Bay and Blanchard Mountain while enjoying world-class sunsets from the covered decks. The two-story Craftsman-style home, complete with two primary bedroom suites (one on each level), is perfection with no detail overlooked. Outside, find professional landscaping and a 3200 square foot shop with space for 6 vehicles and all your projects and toys. There is ADU potential too, with an upper loft already constructed in the shop. Don't miss this legacy property in sought-after Bow!

Three quarter acre property on Fir Island with older home, detached garage and shop! House has been converted into two units, shop has been converted into living space. Convenient to I-5 and surrounded by open farmland with some of the best soils in the state! House needs updating, bring you toolkit and polish it up! Great potential!

Great chance to own 5.86 acres near Lake McMurray with septic installed. Great property for recreation or investment. Property will require a rain catchment system for water if buyer intends to build. Lot cert on file, septic as built and permit recorded online. Septic installed, but in unknown condition. Buyer to verify all to buyer's satisfaction.

Bring your imagination. This property provides the most tranquil setting. Enjoy all nature has to offer on your private 6.2 acres. This 1995 manufactured home has plenty of space, with well-sized bedrooms and two full baths. The kitchen provides a large eating area. The front deck provides plenty of room for entertainment. There is a 20X30 metal shop with a metal roof that includes a 10X10 backroom with a bath. The property also boasts a woodshed, gazebo, play equipment and a chicken coop. There are great recreational areas nearby, and only a short drive to the town of Sedro-Wooley and all the conveniences. Welcome Home!

Discover this extraordinary custom-built luxury home, featuring 3461 sqft on a half-acre landscaped lot offering privacy and Northwest living. The main floor boasts a spacious open great room with vaulted ceilings, skylights, and expansive views. The chef's kitchen includes custom cabinets, pull-outs, under-counter lighting, a custom tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry. The primary suite offers a grand custom tile shower, spacious walk-in closet, and champagne bronze fixtures. Downstairs features a media room, office, full bath, and flex room/ 4th bedroom. Outside, enjoy a fenced yard with a covered heated patio, gas BBQ, fire pit, and fenced yard. Includes a massive four-car garage. Ideal for luxury seekers in a serene setting.

Wow! One of these condos rarely hit the market! This condo has just been redone with new interior paint, new vinyl plank flooring, new heaters, new bath, new 2 faux wood blinds throughout. Interbay is a condo association with 12 units, each with a single car garage and storage room. This unit is 2 bedrooms, 1 bath located on the main level. The kitchen offers refrigerator, dishwasher, stove and the laundry includes the washer and dryer. There is a nice covered patio plus a 23' dock!! Priced to sell!

Welcome to your new home! This delightful 773 square-foot home is perfect for those seeking a cozy and charming living space. Nestled in the heart of Sedro-Woolley this 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers both comfort and convenience. Step into the kitchen that perfectly combines charm and functionality. With tons of natural light and a quaint breakfast nook its perfect for your morning coffee. Step outside to your fully fenced yard, plenty of room for play and relaxation. The property also features a small one car garage and secure alley access parking, offering a discreet and reliable place for parking your vehicles. This home has it all! Come check it out today!

This charming country rambler is located on acreage in a beautiful setting. It has an oversized detached garage/shop that can be used for a variety of purposes. The house has a friendly floor plan with unlimited potential, bright and cheery natural lighting, natural stonework for the fireplace surround, and a country kitchen with walk-in storage. The custom vaulted ceiling and large windows cannot be substituted. There is a second full bath that is patially completed. This home has enormous potential for anyone willing to take on a little work and customize to your tastes and budget.

Showcase lot! Prime waterfront living on this nearly acre property, boasting over 200 feet of coveted low bank waterfront. Every room positioned to capture breathtaking views from the majestic Rainbow Bridge to the tranquil south end of the Swinomish Channel. Entertain with ease in the inviting great room, ideal for hosting gatherings or unwinding with loved ones. 3 bedroom rambler w/ oversized primary + 2 additional bedrooms flexible for crafting or office space. Wrap around deck & private patio creates an unforgettable backdrop for al fresco dining & sunset cocktails. The lower level casita retreat offers privacy & flex-space with a bedroom, twin day beds, bathroom & kitchenette. Nestled on a mature, private lot, this gem is a rare find.

Discover a picturesque retreat in Anacortes overlooking Similk Bay with stunning golf course, mountain, and wetland views. Bamboo flooring and heated tile create warmth and comfort throughout. The primary suite occupies the entire upper floor, featuring a vaulted ceiling, private deck, and a cozy fireplace. French doors lead to the ensuite bath, boasting a soaking tub, double vanity, and an enormous walk-in closet. The main floor offers open concept living, kitchen, & dining spaces. Stay comfortable year-round with a mini split ductless system, & store your outdoor gear in the 10x18 shed. Quick stroll to the beach plus close to state parks, this home embodies both luxury and convenience in an idyllic coastal setting.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Discover a rare fee simple gem in LaConner with stunning bay views. This charming home features a main floor master suite for ultimate convenience, while the upper level offers two additional bedrooms, half bath and a versatile bonus room, ideal for guests. Inside, you'll find beautiful hardwood floors and the cozy ambiance of a wood-burning stove. Enjoy a spacious updated kitchen w/newer appliances and updated baths on both levels. The home opens up to two large new decks (hello summer), perfect for entertaining or enjoying peaceful moments surrounded by gorgeous landscaping as well as a detached studio perfect for guests, a home office, or a creative space. The property includes access to the use of Hope Island amenities.

This is the one you've been waiting for! Burlington's Best home is situated on a quiet corner lot within walking distance of shopping, schools, transit, the neighborhood park, and more. Charming elegance of the past meets modern style of today - with floors and roof having been updated recently, as well as new paint, new cabinets/countertops, new light fixtures, and a new sewer line! The large kitchen affords a small eating space, with room for a dining table in the family room. Natural light pours into the bedrooms and throughout the house! Every square foot has been thoughtfully cared for with a purpose in this cozy space. Mature foliage out front and in the yard provides plenty of opportunity for garden dreams to come true. Welcome Home!

Unlock the potential for sweat equity with this fantastic opportunity! Nestled near downtown Anacortes, this rare find boasts a sprawling double-sized corner lot w/ alley access, offering endless possibilities. A detached garage and shop add further value, ideal for an ADU unit or second home. Step into history w/ this spacious historic home featuring a welcoming covered front porch. A large main-level bedroom complemented by three additional generous bedrooms upstairs, plus the convenience of two full baths. Blocks away from schools, dining & shopping, swift access to the waterfront & marina. Don't miss this remarkable opportunity to tailor-make your dream home!

Updated, move-in ready 1939 charmer in desirable Hillcrest neighborhood. Ideally located on a level lot close to parks, schools, medical, shopping, & dining, easy access to I-5. This adorable bungalow-style home retains original character w/hardwood floors, built-in storage in breakfast room & hall, and beautiful coved ceilings, and has been updated where it counts: Newer furnace & roof, cement-board siding, new windows, tankless water heater, granite counters & stainless appliances in the kitchen, beautifully tiled bathroom. Spacious primary suite with sitting room, multiple closets, private 3/4 bath. Sunroom (possible 3rd bedroom) leads to covered patio, fenced yard, hot tub, new storage shed. Attached garage, low maintenance fenced yard.

Enjoy spectacular sunsets over Langley Bay, Burrows Bay, and the San Juan Islands from this custom-built home. Revel in the elegance of coffered ceilings in the living room, complemented by a stone fireplace & a gourmet kitchen perfect for culinary delights. Retreat to the primary bedroom boasting a luxurious en suite bath and direct deck access. The lower level offers entertainment with a theatre room, a rec room with a kitchenette, and 2 guest bedrooms. Outside, enjoy manicured grounds with low maintenance landscaping & a separate RV garage. Private community beach access & potential moorage for added convenience and leisure. This is more than just a home; it's a sanctuary where every detail is crafted for your utmost comfort & enjoyment.

Experience waterfront living at its finest in Shelter Bay's leased land property on a serene canal with views of Rainbow Bridge and La Conner. This updated home boasts modern features like solar blinds, refreshed window and door trim inside and out, and a fresh coat of paint. Enjoy a spacious patio right at the water's edge, perfect for year around enjoyment & entertaining. The landscaped yard enhances the outdoor charm, complemented by a fenced side yard housing a relaxing hot tub. Shelter Bay offers an array of amenities including a marina, pool, sports courts, beach access, and more, ensuring a vibrant coastal lifestyle awaits you. Discover a lifestyle of comfort and leisure in this waterfront gem.

Discover the perfect spot for your camper, RV, or a manufactured home in the Cape Horn community. This versatile lot is ideal for year-round living or as a weekend getaway. With water and electricity conveniently available at the street, setting up is a breeze. Enjoy easy access to the stunning Skagit River, perfect for fishing enthusiasts and nature lovers. The community park enhances your experience with amenities like a playground, a gazebo with picnic tables, a basketball court, making it perfect for gatherings and leisurely activities. Explore the numerous nearby trails and immerse yourself in the natural beauty of the Pacific NW. Build your dream home & savor all that this enchanting location has to offer. Your adventure begins here!

RARE OPPORTUNITY for Investors or primary residence! This well cared for Duplex is located on beautiful lot w/a MASSIVE 1800sqft shop and 2 car garage w/office. Unit 1 is owner occupied with 2 beds, .75bath, bonus room, spacious living room, kitchen and utility room/mud room. Pellet stove to keep you warm in winter and ceiling fans and window A/C unit to cool you down in summer. Unit 2 with long-term tenant has 1 bed with patio access, kitchen with eating area 1 bath. Spacious backyard w/beautiful garden beds, fruit trees, partially fenced w/shop access through gate. Shop has plenty of storage, work benches and room for all your toys and projects. 2 car garage w/generous storage throughout leads to office or craft space. Great location!

Gorgeous dream home on an acre overlooking Swinomish Channel, Skagit farmland, Mt. Baker & the Cascades. Watch the boats glide by from your covered front porch; swans & snow geese from the back. Light, bright, & airy, this 3470/sf 3 bed/3 bath home is too perfect to describe. Soaring vaulted ceiling in the great room. Stunning kitchen w/big center island w/seating on 2 sides, gas range, pantry. Primary retreat on main floor w/spa-inspired 5 piece bath. Home office. Upstairs is a bonus room w/wet bar, 2 generously sized guest rooms - w/an adorable secret room shared between - and full bath. Geothermal heat/cooling. RV parking. Shed & chicken coop. Beautiful home w/fantastic views, level lot, room for living & entertaining- it's all here!

Welcome HOME to this exquisite Historic Beauty!! A perfect blend of old charm character from the past & gorgeous modern upgrades! Like stepping into a designer magazine! Immaculately cared for throughout! Be greeted by a classic covered porch. As you enter find gorgeous original hardwood floors restored to their former glamor! NEW interior features include a range, double ovens, countertops, dishwasher, kitchen floors & carpet! Freshly painted inside & out! Custom upgraded bathrooms provide a spa-like experience. Escape to the outdoor oasis with perfectly manicured lawns, gardens & deck making a great space for summertime entertaining! NEW concrete patio & driveway! Nestled in a quiet neighborhood yet minutes from all life's amenities!

Make your small town home dreams come true w/ this BEAUTIFUL completely remodeled cape cod home! Stay cool in this summers heat w/ the newly installed A/C. Yes this 1901 home has A/C, new plumbing, electrical, appliances, finishes, & professionally landscaped. Enjoy evenings or mornings on either one of the beautiful private patios. Have fun on the finished w/ wood chips play ground that stays (Trampoline included!)! All of your storage needs are covered w/ a convenient shed off the driveway in the back alley for private parking. Enjoy the RV parking for additional space. Mature apple & plum trees are producing fruit for you to enjoy each year! The home has a main floor primary bedroom. Bonus loft space upstairs and 2 additional bedrooms!

Welcome to this inviting one-level home located in the sought-after Vedere Terrace neighborhood. This charming property features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths and is situated on a peaceful street. Enjoy a spacious living area, a convenient kitchen with stainless appliances, and a lovely dining area perfect for gatherings. Hardwood flooring in the living spaces. The generous primary suite is thoughtfully separated from the other bedrooms to ensure privacy. Outside, relax on the large deck with a fenced yard, ideal for enjoying beautiful summer evenings. Even a peek-a-boo view of the farmlands. An attached garage & additional off-street parking offers convenience at your doorstep. Located close to I-5, it offers easy access for commuters.

Welcome to your dream home in Daycreek! This gem is a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom and offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. With vaulted ceilings and a free-standing propane fireplace to keep you warm. Sitting on 6+ acres, with seven covered parking areas, you'll have ample space for all your vehicles and toys. Animal lovers will appreciate the one-stall barn and large fenced area, perfect for horses or other pets. Entertain with ease using the smoker for BBQ fun, relax in the hot tub, or tackle any project in the large shop. Large blueberry bushes and raspberry plants to snack on. So much room a garden could be added! Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a versatile property that meets all your needs.

Newly installed 30-year roof with transferable warranty! NEW vinyl planking floors, paint throughout, sink & faucet in the kitchen. Newer dishwasher and stove. Light and bright, this two-bedroom home lives large with an open concept kitchen, dining room and great room which includes vaulted ceilings, ceiling fan and built in bookshelves in kitchen and dining room. In home washer and dryer make this home complete. Detached one car garage with parking in front of garage and an assigned spot (3 spots total). Covered front & back porch. Relax at the end of the day enjoying the view and sounds of nature emanating from the expansive green space behind the home. Truly a delightful place to call home with yardwork included in your HOA dues.

Wonderful & beautiful custom designed home in the Skyline. No steps home offers breath-taking 180' panorama west views from the Olympics all the way to Canada! Upon entering the home, one is greeted with a sense of calm & serenity, creating an atmosphere conducive to relaxation. The house features a large office space, wide hallways and 36 solid doors offering easy access throughout. A spacious parking area w/ boat/RV parking plus an insulated oversized 3-car garage. Gorgeous landscaped yard further enhances the appeal of the home, creating a outdoor space to enjoy & unwind. This residence presents an opportunity to own a showcase home in a desirable location. Close to Skyline Marina, Washington Park and San Juan's Is ferry terminal
